DYSART
v.
CUMMINGS. No. 132A07. Supreme Court of North Carolina. April 23, 2007. John Walter Bryant, Raleigh, for Cummings.

The following order has been entered on the motion filed on the 20th day of April 2007 by Plaintiffs for Extension of Time to File Brief:

"Motion Allowed. Plaintiffs shall have up to and including the 13th day of June 2007 to file and serve his/her brief with this Court. By order of the Court in conference this the 23rd day of April 2007."
